UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 1611
1 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
2 Kentucky:
3 Section 1. The members of the Senate hereby express their most profound
4 sympathy upon the passing of Charles William Kennedy and extend heartfelt
5 condolences to his family, friends, and community.
6 Section 2. When the Senate adjourns this day, it does so in honor and loving
7 memory of Charles William Kennedy.
8 Section 3. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
9 Resolution to Senator Gerald Neal for delivery to the family.
